mal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實要集會根本唔撚洗有不反對通知書"},{"pid":"193284489fb5c9115052e1732dd4752ed6e519b2","tid":1325224,"uid":163819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:55:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d73597dda874e4082fbea2599fc17affc1d053c","tid":1325224,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:55:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有人大狀出黎講多D?<br />\n楊大狀出黎幫手解釋下?</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"4b117a15b6b890554a190f2debfc1c95dcc38f6a","tid":1325224,"uid":266643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"18df5038f454c5b3ec936d482675e908ad975fa3","tid":1325224,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6a3a8e702bf606a94cc921bd9b03f05a191d448","tid":1325224,"uid":14503,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">根本和理非贏曬, 幾時遊行都得!!!<br />\n<br />\n所謂&quot;不反對通知書&quot;係警察自己set既deadline, deadline後會以武力驅散&quot;勇武派&quot; 如果係和理非既話佢地都唔可以驅散。<br />\n<br />\ndeadline後警察會挑釁和理非令到部份人變激進, 一爆衝突先可以出師有名咁清場, 所以警察唔可以驅散聖詩派。<br />\n<br />\n早幾日沙田商場事件警察係自己set既deadline前有所行動其實已經証明&quot;不反對通知書&quot;如同虛設<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次警察想人地以為自己可以任意驅散和理非所以索性唔發不反對通知書!!!</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">終院已經講左, 警察唔可以因為政要唔想聽到反對聲音以去阻止人集會, 如果咁既情況下拘捕人=非法拘捕</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"係喎，之前612啲聖詩派佢冇暴力驅趕到"},{"pid":"4c8322558d6ad69bbdec8185addd7a457fb67cb2","tid":1325224,"uid":126412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:57:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21d43f27d1d4d5c110eed8775ff5433180ebd9c6","tid":1325224,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:57:45.000Z","msg":"到時肯定釋法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d4cdf0e55f4e9f7384370769238af8f1cf396f","tid":1325224,"uid":267328,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ea86d472742c35b5c66098cd69895350419e280","tid":1325224,"uid":114537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"同問 非法集結 同 集會自由 有無衝突？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"冇<br />\n非法集結<br />\n(1)凡有3人或多於3人集結在一起，作出擾亂秩序的行為或作出帶有威嚇性、侮辱性或挑撥性的行為，意圖導致或相當可能導致任何人合理地害怕如此集結的人會破壞社會安寧，或害怕他們會藉以上的行為激使其他人破壞社會安寧，他們即屬非法集結。  (由1970年第31號第11條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n你冇作出擾亂秩序的行為，即使冇不反對通知書，亦唔算非法集結。和理非作用就係呢度發揮。"},{"pid":"4864cab31587c2f28f11bc0a89335dfcafb16732","tid":1325224,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:09:49.000Z","msg":"一定出"},{"pid":"edb4723bc532044ceea1df2aed87d5e8e6172bf4","tid":1325224,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3086b9a6e9f9f769e637ba9db15f9f9d056efb36","tid":1325224,"uid":122676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1658179bf8123354dc40d3d6d289920c214598a5","tid":1325224,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942e87caafd634ed6647fff7ed4a74d3479f1cf4","tid":1325224,"uid":131122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:30:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">fb ig wtsapp telegram<br />\n個個都要做文宣！！！！<br />\n出個post都唔肯既我馬上屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"19f3141644b2b37c0eb3b92811bddb4586abf192","tid":1325224,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4826e1db655e970cb45d260f2e35c1f1351ad514","tid":1325224,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited